Locust Swarm

Through this potent charm, the druid summons a
ravenous swarm of locusts to the area.  The insects
will bite and torment creatures, slipping into the
gaps in armor; at the same time, they will eat all
of the food they can find.  Only druids and their
summoned or charmed followers are protected against
their rampage.

Command: lswarm
Base Cost: 120 SP
Base Recovery: long
Base Effect: damage (moderate, area)
Base Duration: instant
Guild Level: 17
